rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d655ce0abed1b4b67c54fb0d7b6386cdb2c7177","tid":2451424,"uid":127815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:30:14.000Z","msg":"真係無人識？或者有呢個病？Lady Gaga都係呢個病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89d850436dce73dcd36f1c7686e387dc72b96ba","tid":2451424,"uid":364041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"去操下肌肉就冇事"},{"pid":"46c096fba6f1fb752ce3de34f192bdf59d488a4a","tid":2451424,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多啲係點痛法？<br />\n抽住抽住？"},{"pid":"1dc4d4198a66a69390305e6fb9ae30c0c05da05c","tid":2451424,"uid":127815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46c096fba6f1fb752ce3de34f192bdf59d488a4a","tid":2451424,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多啲係點痛法？<br />\n抽住抽住？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:42:00.000Z","msg":"頸係俾針吉咁刺痛，有時會痛到訓唔到要食安眠藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩邊腳踭果種痛就唔識講 <br />\n係好似兩邊腳踭同時撞左埋去鐵櫃果一下痛，但係長期都係咁樣痛法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇左無數個骨科醫生都話唔係足底筋膜炎 唔係骨刺 照晒野乜都唔係 發炎都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉介左睇痛症科都話唔知咩原因<br />\n但有食緊醫生開嘅神經痛藥<br />\n唔肯定有無幫助<br />\n因為一路食住但最近又痛返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbb6c2305cff455699d9b680256eb1e084db642","tid":2451424,"uid":127815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b89d850436dce73dcd36f1c7686e387dc72b96ba","tid":2451424,"uid":364041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"去操下肌肉就冇事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"但腳踭長期痛 操唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d31fdab2c49e152e0e94a6d6d13d83b2c8e6f7","tid":2451424,"uid":364041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfbb6c2305cff455699d9b680256eb1e084db642","tid":2451424,"uid":127815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b89d850436dce73dcd36f1c7686e387dc72b96ba","tid":2451424,"uid":364041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"去操下肌肉就冇事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"但腳踭長期痛 操唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16:04: